title: Evelynn coaching, Free for anybody that wants it.

embed.description: Zealitee / Diamond 2 24LP / 225W 183L Win Ratio 55% / Taliyah - 29W 15L Win Ratio 66%, Fiora - 9W 8L Win Ratio 53%, Gangplank - 6W 9L Win Ratio 40%, Jayce - 9W 5L Win Ratio 64%, Morgana - 7W 7L Win Ratio 50%

body:
With the recent release of the Evelynn rework and her rising popularity in soloqueue there are now alot of new players trying to learn the agony's embrace.
I feel like I have a solid grasp of the new Eve and I would love to share that with anybody that feels like they need help.
Feel free to add me in game or join the discord that I setup and you can find me there! 
https://discord.gg/mjshShQ

Merry Christmas guys, hope you had a great day.
